117
00:10:12,479 --> 00:10:14,350
Kita hanya bisa sejauh itu.

118
00:10:15,350 --> 00:10:16,850
Kenapa bukan urusanku?

119
00:10:17,050 --> 00:10:19,619
Seperti katamu, kita harus mempertahankan situasi ini.

120
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,420
