178
00:13:55,499 --> 00:13:57,940
- Aku melihat semuanya.
- Apa maksudmu?

179
00:13:58,499 --> 00:14:00,710
Di upacara pertunangan Soo Ryeon,

180
00:14:01,369 --> 00:14:02,540
